title: Pre-UFYB 11: All about Avoidance
itunes:title: Pre-UFYB 11: All about Avoidance
description:
On this episode, we explore what makes you avoid tasks and how to change that habit. Join us on the show as I lay out a step-by-step process that will help you deal with any task you’re avoiding and finally get it done!

Get full show notes and more information here: http://bit.ly/2tmkwxs
